reviews.textTranslated:
I had to organise an end of tenancy clean at the very last minute and reached out to K Cleaning Solutions. Honestly, I didn‚Äôt expect them to respond so quickly but they were at my place within an hour.

From the moment they arrived, they were professional and got straight into the job. What really stood out was the attention to detail. This was not just a surface clean, they went deep. Every area was properly done from the kitchen spaces to the bathroom fittings, walls, floors and even those small spots most people would miss during a rushed job.

After the clean, they did not just pack up and leave. They walked me through everything they had done and explained each area along with the extra work they put in to make sure the place met end of tenancy standards. That gave me real confidence in the quality of the job.

The before and after difference was honestly amazing. The place looked refreshed and ready for handover. On top of that, they went the extra mile and even offered a discount which I really appreciated given how last minute the booking was.

Very professional, responsive and easy to deal with. I am genuinely happy with the outcome and would definitely recommend K Cleaning Solutions to anyone needing a reliable clean, especially under time pressure.
